#. Tag: title
#: editors-note.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note from the Editors"
msgstr "Napomena editora"

#. Tag: para
#: editors-note.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As you may notice, this handbook is written by various authors. The draft "
"explanation of new features is done by the developers on the krusader-devel "
"mailinglist, the editors add this information in this handbook. We have "
"taken much care in ensuring technical and vocabulary consistency. The "
"authors write in English even though it is not their native language; "
"therefore, you may notice strange sentence constructions. Do not hesitate to "
"let us know, if something is not clear to you."
msgstr ""
"Kao što ste primijetili, ova knjiga je napisana od različitih autora.  Nacrt "
"objašnjena novih značajki je napravljen od developera na krusader-devel "
"mejling listi, urednici su dodali ovu informaciju priručniku. Preduzeli smo "
"dosta brige da osiguramo tehničku i vokabularsku tačnost. Autori pišu na "
"Engleskom iako to nije njihov maternji jezik; stoga možete primijetiti neke "
"čudne konstrukcije. Ne ustručavajte se da nam se javite, ako nešto nije "
"jasno."

#. Tag: para
#: editors-note.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An open source project's greatest strength is derived from getting user "
"feedback. That is why we would love to hear what you have to say. "
"<emphasis>Documentation contributors are always welcome!</emphasis>, since "
"this is a time consuming task. If you have ideas on how to improve the "
"content, if you would like to write about an undocumented &krusader; "
"feature, or if you have comments or suggestions about the &krusader; "
"Handbook, please let us know. You can contact us even if you find typos!"
msgstr ""
"U programu otvorenog koda najveća snage je u povratnim informacijama Zato bi "
"voljeli da čujemo šta vi imate da kažete. <emphasis>Dokumentacijski "
"saradnici su uvijek dobro došli</emphasis>,jer je ovo dugotrajan posao. Ako "
"imate ideja kako da poboljšamo sadržaj ili da pišete nenapisane dokumente "
"&krusader; ubuduće,Ili ako imate bilo kakvih sugestija &krusader; priručnik, "
"molimo vas da nas obavijestite. Možete nas kontaktirati čak i ako nađete "
"pravopisne greške."

#. Tag: para
#: editors-note.docbook:27
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For information about the &krusader; documentation project, please "
#| "contact the &krusader; documentation coordinator, Frank Schoolmeesters "
#| "<email>frank_schoolmeesters * yahoo.com</email>."
msgid ""
"For information about the &krusader; documentation project, please contact "
"the &krusader; documentation coordinator, Yuri Chornoivan <email>yurchor@ukr."
"net</email>."
msgstr ""
"Za informacije o  &krusader; dokumentacijskim projektima, molimo vas "
"kontaktirajte &krusader; dokumentacijskog koordinatora, Franka "
"Schoolmeestersa <email>frank_schoolmeesters * yahoo.com</email>."

#. Tag: para
#: editors-note.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "This handbook is available in several formats."
msgstr "Ovaj priručnik je dostupan u više formata."

